好離開我<br />\n可唔可以返嚟我身邊<br />\n無咗你我就無咗成個世界<br />\n可唔可以比我繼續照顧你保護你"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T04:45:34.000Z","msg":"你好，這是《自殺．自療．互助舍》。看來你已累積了不少負面情緒，是嗎？人就好像氣球一樣，若積存的鬱結和壓力太多，便會有爆發的一天。何不暫時停一停，到我們的網站       <a href=\"http://www.help4suicide.com.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.help4suicide.com.hk&d=tWDRN%2F4Vza2V0D3%2FQI2QfYkJ8G0wCzjK2GZdEgWvKr0%3D&h=e3f45b1a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>       。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》&quot;"},{"pid":"0a2dc33afc484b3293929829c3b182d9d675e2c3","tid":2078614,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"866372ebe52aa21f45ec4193aaa544eeb4ee3b27","tid":2078614,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a2dc33afc484b3293929829c3b182d9d675e2c3","tid":2078614,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"一齊支持大組長"},{"pid":"498878ca9d46adaa3701f076fa5d5d961e84c51f","tid":2078614,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"866372ebe52aa21f45ec4193aaa544eeb4ee3b27","tid":2078614,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a2dc33afc484b3293929829c3b182d9d675e2c3","tid":2078614,"uid":199279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:50:38.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T08:51:56.000Z","msg":"一齊支持大組長"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-29T09:13:40.000Z","msg":"支持大組長屌柒個exex<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e52ef80c5cfb122a6ac463d29d4c